		"description": "<p>You reach into your natural connection with the fey realms and summon a faithful steed or companion. As an action, you may summon a fey spirit that takes the form of a @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-monsters.Actor.uBRfmk9d5mJE4z60]{Corgi}. If you are Tiny, you may use the corgi as a mount. If you are larger, the corgi functions as a familiar. If the corgi is reduced to 0 hit points, it disappears, and you must use your action to re-summon it. You may also dismiss the corgi as a bonus action.</p>",
